{"tid":2490927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6歲孫求爺爺購物遭拒趴地發脾氣　司機以為是膠袋直接開車輾過","createTime":"2021-04-16T03:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T03:54:58.000Z","uid":271829,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6399e1afe5e4bad7deaffd2842ca0c60d7fbff","tid":2490927,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/car_thumb_20210416_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2Fcar_thumb_20210416_J_1024.jpg&h=9d0dae43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 6歲孫求爺爺購物遭拒趴地發脾氣，司機以為是膠袋直接開車輾過。<br />\n<br />\n不少孩子以為發脾氣便會獲得父母的注意，但一不留神便可能發生意外。內地一名6歲男童求爺爺購物不果，竟趴在地下發脾氣耍賴，沒想到下一秒被一輛車駛近，司機以為是黑色膠袋直接輾過，男童隨即送院救治，幸運只有臉部擦傷及左腿骨折，生命沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2F1_1024.jpg&h=079ff044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 男童求爺爺到超級市場購物不果趴到。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n綜合內體媒體報道，事發在4月2日的浙江，一名6歲男童欲想到超級市場購物，卻遭到爺爺拒絕，於是他趴在地上發脾氣，爺爺不以為意，認為他孫子鬧一會便會沒事，他便離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n從閉路電視可見，正當男童在地下哭鬧時，下一秒一輛黑色車駛經該路段，司機沒有煞車，直接輾過男童，及後整個身體消失在畫面中。及後，爺爺才跑回現場，表現非常慌張地責怪司機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2F2_1024.jpg&h=ba559c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男童趴地發脾氣。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/4213_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2F4213_1024.jpg&h=41cb0439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色車輛駛近男童。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2F3_1024.jpg&h=67c3450f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機立刻下車檢查，發現男童被捲入車底。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n司機以為是膠袋開車輾過<br />\n司機向媒體表示，當時以為地下有一個黑色膠袋，便不經意地直接駛過，直到感覺顛頗才下車查看，驚覺自己輾過一名男童。男童隨即被送院治療，幸得臉部擦傷、左腿骨折，並無生命危險。據悉，是次事故司機要負主要責任，男童的監護人要負次要責任，而男童則無責任。"},{"pid":"4a553b14664b9fef52c3b64efe378b2bd04c74c3","tid":2490927,"uid":199893,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"男童冇責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係嘅 已經被人碌咗嘢 唔使再負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d35d566259374bc410413e21a80d3ffe18782e","tid":2490927,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6399e1afe5e4bad7deaffd2842ca0c60d7fbff","tid":2490927,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/car_thumb_20210416_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2930000%2F2933493%2Fcar_thumb_20210416_J_1024.jpg&h=9d0dae43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 6歲孫求爺爺購物遭拒趴地發脾氣，司機以為是膠袋直接開車輾過。<br />\n<br />\n不少孩子以為發脾氣便會獲得父母的注意，但一不留神便可能發生意外。內地一名6歲男童求爺爺購物不果，竟趴在地下發脾氣耍賴，沒想到下一秒被一輛車駛近，司機以為是黑色膠袋直接輾過，男童隨即送院救治，幸運只有臉部擦傷及左腿骨折，生命沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2930000/2933493/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.